  </header>

  <main class="relative flex w-full flex-col gap-10 overflow-hidden bg-gray-950 py-16 lg:gap-24">
    <section class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-xl flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center lg:flex-row">
      <div class="max-w-xl p-6 sm:p-10 lg:max-w-none xl:p-24">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold">
          Missing controllers
